WEBVTT

23:59:37.240 --> 23:59:40.410
<i>♪ We are the Crystal Gems, ♪</i>

23:59:40.411 --> 23:59:43.580
<i> # we'll always save the day, #</i>

23:59:43.590 --> 23:59:48.250
<i>♪ and if you think we can't,
we'll always find a way, ♪</i>

23:59:48.710 --> 23:59:53.620
<i>♪ that's why the people
of this world believe in, ♪</i>

23:59:54.150 --> 23:59:59.150
<i>♪ Garnet, Amethyst, and Pearl...
and Steven! ♪</i>

23:59:59.510 --> 00:02.630
<b>1x06 - "Cat Fingers"</b>

00:03.510 --> 00:06.290
Almost done. 
Steven, get the hubcaps.

00:06.740 --> 00:07.540
Hubbin' it up!

00:09.500 --> 00:12.560
Hub it good. 
This is a high-profile job.

00:12.740 --> 00:14.870
You mean 'cause it's
the Mayor's election-mobile?

00:15.130 --> 00:17.890
If we do this right, we
might get political favors.

00:18.140 --> 00:20.860
I'm not sure what
that is, but I like it.

00:26.240 --> 00:27.690
Hey, hey, hey!

00:27.725 --> 00:30.860
I'm not paying for
father-son bonding here.

00:32.290 --> 00:35.200
- Universe! Control that kid!
- Steven!

00:35.630 --> 00:39.100
I'm sorry, Mayor Dewey.
Uh, this one's on the house.

00:39.680 --> 00:41.600
On the house, eh?

00:42.070 --> 00:44.530
I like the way you do
business, Universe.

00:45.900 --> 00:50.140
<i>Mayor Dewey! 
Mayor Dewey!</i>

00:50.210 --> 00:52.210
Political favors!

00:52.480 --> 00:55.500
Ah, you rascal. Enough
with the hose fights.

00:55.535 --> 00:56.620
Ah, okay.

00:58.130 --> 00:58.850
What the...

01:00.430 --> 01:01.310
Whoa!

01:03.780 --> 01:05.340
What is with this cat?

01:07.860 --> 01:10.980
- Ha-ha! Got you guys.
- Amethyst!

01:11.070 --> 01:13.280
Uh, pretty cool, Amethyst.

01:13.520 --> 01:16.410
Really cool. I wish I could
shapeshift like you.

01:16.560 --> 01:17.720
You could probably learn.

01:17.890 --> 01:18.400
Really?

01:18.780 --> 01:20.380
Sure. You got a Gem.

01:20.410 --> 01:23.120
Whoa! Magic stuff.
Should I get out of here?

01:23.150 --> 01:24.650
Is there gonna be an explosion?

01:24.860 --> 01:26.450
Ah, it's  no big deal, Dad.

01:26.660 --> 01:28.980
Yeah, it's fuuuun.

01:30.490 --> 01:31.740
<i>Hey, Pearl.</i>

01:34.700 --> 01:37.010
- Do more!
- Check it out.

01:42.380 --> 01:45.310
- Whoa!
- Amethyst, you are overdoing it.

01:45.460 --> 01:47.660
Uh, chill it, dude.

01:47.950 --> 01:51.250
Just because you can shapeshift
doesn't mean you should.

01:51.390 --> 01:53.740
- Can you shapeshift?
- Well, of course...

01:53.775 --> 01:58.110
Well, of course I can. I'm perfect.
Whomp! Whomp!

01:58.950 --> 02:01.790
All Gems have
shapeshift powers, Steven.

02:02.070 --> 02:06.330
We can turn into objects, we can
change parts of our bodies, or...

02:06.770 --> 02:07.840
we could do that.

02:08.110 --> 02:09.229
Whomp! Whomp!

02:09.389 --> 02:10.470
I want to try it all!

02:10.770 --> 02:13.510
Don't bite off more than
you can chew, Steven.

02:13.511 --> 02:16.239
- Whomp! Whomp!
- Ugh!

02:17.440 --> 02:20.300
All right! Show me how to
change into a huge lion!

02:20.630 --> 02:23.010
Actually, for once, Pearl is right.

02:23.350 --> 02:26.180
If you're gonna do this, you gotta
start with something easy.

02:26.510 --> 02:28.090
Like that cat you turned into?

02:28.430 --> 02:30.460
That sounds good.
Now follow my lead.

02:31.470 --> 02:35.780
First: think of what you wanna
be, and then just shake it out.

02:37.320 --> 02:39.510
See?
Now your turn.

02:39.830 --> 02:40.600
Okay.

02:41.810 --> 02:44.230
Ca-a-a-a-a-t.

02:44.380 --> 02:47.470
Nah, you're too tense.
Just relax and feel it.

02:49.070 --> 02:50.632
Biorhythms, yo'.

02:50.670 --> 02:53.580
Fe-e-e-e-el it.

02:54.050 --> 02:57.030
Eeeh, if you are not
ready, we can try later.

02:57.130 --> 02:58.420
No way. I can do it.

03:01.150 --> 03:03.560
Yeah. Yeah.

03:08.140 --> 03:09.610
Well, it was a good try.

03:17.930 --> 03:19.400
This is so cool!

03:19.560 --> 03:23.135
You should go show your Dad.
He's gonna freak out!

03:24.980 --> 03:26.280
<i>Dad, I'm back.</i>

03:26.640 --> 03:29.140
- Hey, Stu-ball.
- Check it out.

03:33.860 --> 03:38.140
- I shapeshifted my finger into a cat.
- Whoa!

03:39.030 --> 03:42.650
Is that a thing you can do now?
That's pretty cool.

03:42.685 --> 03:43.580
I know. Right?

03:43.930 --> 03:46.430
I'm gonna take this show on the road.

03:50.390 --> 03:52.230
<i>That'll be $1.05, Steven.</i>

03:52.680 --> 03:57.180
Mmm, okay. Here's a nickel.
And a buck!

03:58.430 --> 03:59.913
- Whaaaat?
- Whaaaat?

04:00.960 --> 04:02.900
Oh, Steven, that's adorable.

04:05.830 --> 04:09.500
- Are you making it purr?
- It kind of does what it wants.

04:09.710 --> 04:10.540
Really?

04:12.202 --> 04:15.031
- Ow!
- See what I mean?

04:15.040 --> 04:18.010
- Bad cat finger!
- Ah, I'm sure it just wants to play.

04:18.500 --> 04:21.570
You are right!
And he doesn't have any friends.

04:21.820 --> 04:25.619
Oh, my gosh!
"It's just like you, Steven."

