04:38.480 --> 04:39.510
Hey, Petey!

04:40.230 --> 04:42.540
Whoa! 
You work the deep fryer now?

04:42.890 --> 04:44.130
Make me some fry bits.

04:44.440 --> 04:48.620
Steven, I take my job seriously.
Please, use the actual menu.

04:48.810 --> 04:52.240
- Give me the bits. The bits!
- All right, listen. 

04:52.275 --> 04:54.370
It'll be over sooner if you
just give him what he wants.

04:55.470 --> 05:01.080
Whoa. Hey, hey! It's not for me.
It's for these guys.

05:03.020 --> 05:07.390
- What the...
- Uh, here's your... bits.

05:10.350 --> 05:13.530
- I can't look away.
- Steven, that is freakish.

05:13.910 --> 05:15.630
No, it's not. It's natural.

05:15.950 --> 05:19.370
Shake... it... out!

05:22.130 --> 05:24.043
- See?
- Wow!

05:24.078 --> 05:26.134
You know who would love this?

05:26.135 --> 05:28.190
Your older brother. Yo, Ronaldo!

05:28.450 --> 05:29.440
What's up, Dad?

05:33.200 --> 05:35.800
I gotta take a pic for
"Keep Beach City weird".

05:37.360 --> 05:39.430
- What's that?
- It's my blog!

05:39.630 --> 05:43.020
Keep... Beach... City... weird.

05:44.410 --> 05:45.550
Can I see the picture?

05:47.340 --> 05:49.670
Yikes!
Oh, ooh. Sorry, guys.

05:49.820 --> 05:54.150
I guess cat fingers don't
function well as... fingers.

05:55.740 --> 05:58.000
Shh!
I'm just getting a snack.

06:02.080 --> 06:05.715
- Whoa!
- Steven! Need some help?

06:05.920 --> 06:07.580
Nah, it's cool.

06:08.170 --> 06:10.460
Oh, good. See you later then.

06:10.720 --> 06:11.310
Huh?

06:11.820 --> 06:15.550
We're taking the Gem sloop out
to sea to fight a living island.

06:16.180 --> 06:16.590
What?

06:19.310 --> 06:22.450
Uh... Amethyst, wait!

06:23.510 --> 06:26.910
<i>I wanna go on the Gem sloop!
I want to see a living island!</i>

06:27.210 --> 06:28.960
<i>Wait, wait, wait!</i>

06:30.440 --> 06:31.030
Steven!

06:32.260 --> 06:34.510
Come on! You can make it!

06:38.610 --> 06:42.850
- Steven! What's going on?
- Uh... i-it's nothing.

06:42.960 --> 06:45.270
Uh, I just turned all
my fingers into cats.

06:46.340 --> 06:48.220
We have to stay and help Steven.

06:48.370 --> 06:51.210
We can't. This is a
tectonic emergency.

06:51.310 --> 06:52.880
We'll deal with Steven
when we get back.

06:53.680 --> 06:57.700
- Amethyst, I blame you for this!
- Eh, that's fair.

06:59.210 --> 07:03.060
<i>Steven! Just try to stay calm!</i>

07:06.310 --> 07:10.610
Enough! No more cat fingers.
I want Steven fingers!

07:11.210 --> 07:13.652
And I don't mean little
me-heads on fingers.

07:13.653 --> 07:15.280
I mean my regular fingers.

07:25.900 --> 07:26.690
Oh! Stop!

07:31.180 --> 07:34.750
Amethyst! Pearl! Garnet!

07:36.190 --> 07:36.880
Dad!

07:45.000 --> 07:46.840
Hello? Who's there?

07:47.810 --> 07:51.262
We're closed.
Come back tomorrow...

07:55.640 --> 07:56.750
Da-a-ad...

08:02.930 --> 08:05.430
- Steven?
- Dad!

08:08.210 --> 08:11.360
Help! The cat fingers
are taking over my body!

08:13.410 --> 08:13.990
Hold on!

08:15.240 --> 08:18.070
- I'll get you out of there!
- Dad!

08:19.120 --> 08:22.010
No! 
Bad! Bad cat fingers!

08:24.300 --> 08:25.780
Can't you make them go away?

08:25.850 --> 08:28.030
I tried, but it made it worse.

08:29.470 --> 08:33.090
<i>My life is over!
I can't go on magic adventures!</i>

08:33.140 --> 08:34.669
<i>I can't even open the fridge.</i>

08:34.909 --> 08:37.510
And I'll never get to have
another water fight with you, Dad,

08:37.700 --> 08:40.450
'cause these things hate...
water.

08:41.120 --> 08:42.120
They hate water!

08:42.750 --> 08:44.440
Dad, spray me again!

08:54.610 --> 08:56.430
It's not enough water!

08:57.710 --> 08:59.340
Turn on the superwash!

08:59.380 --> 09:01.920
No! I won't do it!
It's too dangerous.

09:02.240 --> 09:05.005
You've got to! I'm a monster!

09:05.006 --> 09:07.770
I'm an adorable cat monster!

09:07.990 --> 09:09.970
No, you're not! You're my son!

09:10.280 --> 09:12.200
Dad, please!

09:46.110 --> 09:46.700
Dad.

09:48.590 --> 09:50.059
We did it.

09:59.170 --> 10:01.960
Steven! 
Okay, let me see it.

10:02.790 --> 10:06.510
Well, you... you... you
got them to go away?

10:07.110 --> 10:12.370
It just goes to show - always listen
to me and never listen to Amethyst.

10:12.650 --> 10:13.340
That's fair.

10:13.790 --> 10:18.240
It goes to show - you should
have a little more faith in Steven.

10:18.680 --> 10:23.823
Yeah, that would've been
a total cat-tastrophe.

10:25.830 --> 10:28.960
But I'm feeling much better meow!

10:30.630 --> 10:33.030
What's the matter?
Cat got your tongue?

10:33.060 --> 10:34.050
Okay, that's enough.

10:34.360 --> 10:36.820
Wait. I've been coming up
with cat jokes all morning.

10:36.980 --> 10:39.580
You guys, I'm feline fine!

10:39.860 --> 10:42.210
Everything's purr-fect!

10:43.050 --> 10:46.110
Oh, come on! 
I'm just kitten around!

